{"color": "green", "emoji": "\ud83d\udcac", "event_type": "Agent Message", "message": "Implemented the developer bootstrap workflow and checkpointed it in commit `b01adfd`. The repo now has a root task runner in [Makefile](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/Makefile), first-run setup in [bootstrap-dev.sh](/Users/kevin/code/stor...", "raw_event": {"item": {"id": "item_87", "text": "Implemented the developer bootstrap workflow and checkpointed it in commit `b01adfd`.\n\nThe repo now has a root task runner in [Makefile](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/Makefile), first-run setup in [bootstrap-dev.sh](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/scripts/bootstrap-dev.sh), a safe data-only reset path in [reset-local-data.sh](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/scripts/reset-local-data.sh), and updated quickstart/workflow docs in [README.md](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/README.md), [infra/compose/README.md](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/infra/compose/README.md), [infra/persistence/README.md](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/infra/persistence/README.md), and [scripts/README.md](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/scripts/README.md). The required reviewer summary was written last to [07-developer-bootstrap-scripts.summary.md](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/prompts/07-developer-bootstrap-scripts.summary.md).\n\nVerification:\n- `bash -n scripts/bootstrap-dev.sh scripts/reset-local-data.sh scripts/dev-compose.sh scripts/install-git-hooks.sh scripts/check-secret-hygiene.sh`\n- `make help`\n- `make bootstrap`\n- `make lint`\n- `make test`\n- `make build`\n- `make check`\n- `make ps`\n- `make down`\n\nOne environment-specific limit showed up during verification: `make up` built and launched Compose correctly, but the backend container exited because the existing local `secrets.yaml` has unsupported legacy keys. I documented that in the summary file. No browser checks were needed because this task did not change UI behavior.", "type": "agent_message"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "task_display_context": {"event_number": 160, "prompt_index": 8, "prompt_name": "07 \u2014 Developer Bootstrap Scripts and Convenience Commands", "prompt_total": 100}, "timestap": "2026-03-31T22:08:04-07:00"}
